JrailsAutoComplete
==================

This plugin adds autocomplete support to jrails, using jquery-ui 1.8rc3.
This plugin works similarly to the original rails auto complete


Example
=======
In the controller you can use the macro function as such

class ExampleController < ApplicationController
    auto_complete_for :fruit, :name

    ...
end

In your view:

<%= javascript_include_tag 'jquery, 'jquery-ui', 'jquery-ui-i18n' %>
...
<%= text_field_with_auto_complete :fruit, :name %>

